{"tid":107861,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我由細到大個願望係成為香港天文台職員","createTime":"2017-02-04T17:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T13:58:45.000Z","uid":45772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0330fa504d1a961640ed24740b6f8a6440d7e4e","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:28:49.000Z","msg":"其實我由細到大對氣象好有興趣，願望係成為香港天文台職員 [[係台長/ (高級)科學主任/ 學術主任呢啲職位，唔係清潔工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ]]<br />\n<br />\n但因為幾個原因令我卻步<br />\n<br />\n1. 數理弱，加上高中冇修M2，入到U讀Science只會比人淘汰<br />\n    而科學主任入職要求係Bachelor 1st/2nd hon grad + master   <br />\n    degree，我冇信心做到<br />\n2. 競爭大，每年幾千個人Science grad，但天文台一年請得咁少<br />\n    人... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 冇後路，如果grad左入唔到天文台就真係要煩搵工煩人工，但我<br />\n    屋企又唔係有錢，所以... 唉<br />\n<br />\n宜家讀緊其他bachelor degree，但我每次諗起呢個夢想都好心up心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜闌人靜發洩下，唔好起底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d96c8c9c62f0176d44d0e4d1347281a3d50bdc","tid":107861,"uid":12140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:41:42.000Z","msg":"數差真係冇乜可能⋯⋯<br />\n節哀順變"},{"pid":"452a3d54b3a4490f9d9662422a48504adfdc1e02","tid":107861,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:49:32.000Z","msg":"天文台冇處女職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4b07781492e8f190d44472d5bf24fe92fd8a47","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數差真係冇乜可能⋯⋯<br />\n節哀順變</blockquote><br />\n狂操卷先Math5 Phy5 <br />\n聽講大學啲數好難好抽像 題目完全冇數字 又冇得操練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3bfe5533d469b7b5f339d63c85fad77fe1f24f","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T17:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天文台冇處女職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e794898f45caaee8509b1230dde51537d8f39174","tid":107861,"uid":80559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過讀完F3 physics後就知自己唔識計physics數 放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有買過d關於雲嘅書睇下咁"},{"pid":"85141b6eca1cb56da4023b93907ac17e886ef36d","tid":107861,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T20:33:16.000Z","msg":"天文台職員工作 係咪得tbb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a747f7a53033655f16965b813d690132e394cb5c","tid":107861,"uid":58671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T21:12:26.000Z","msg":"去做份intern 當完夢囉<br />\n又唔難既"},{"pid":"fc17ad2fda9ab6e3df3b3b0b4c49f74acbab30c6","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T23:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過讀完F3 physics後就知自己唔識計physics數 放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有買過d關於雲嘅書睇下咁</blockquote><br />\n唉  其實Physics幾好玩 不過老師教法都好重要 好多人因為老師教得悶教得差而放棄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好少記雲分類 主要留意熱帶氣旋 同埋學睇500hPa天氣圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c3796a969ec6e6ff68cdcacbfc678a0914b422","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天文台職員工作 係咪得tbb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有好多工種<br />\n有負責寫網站寫app程式<br />\n有負責剪片整graph<br />\n有負責維修雷達<br />\n機場控制塔都好似有天文台職員當值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae23783376810990068b9813fbf4678bc2f9628","tid":107861,"uid":80893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"其實你有冇諗過依份工適唔適合你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e761f85943d45a85146882479540590ed8d281","tid":107861,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過讀完F3 physics後就知自己唔識計physics數 放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有買過d關於雲嘅書睇下咁</blockquote><br />\n唉  其實Physics幾好玩 <span style=\"color: red;\">不過老師教法都好重要</span> 好多人因為老師教得悶教得差而放棄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好少記雲分類 主要留意熱帶氣旋 同埋學睇500hPa天氣圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年中三我物理表現幾好，不過個老師好撚黑我憎，所以就放到最後，結果兩科都係文科<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唯一一理科數學就表現好"},{"pid":"4a6c071fade70e12912f93ff24d556ec8082b87d","tid":107861,"uid":35499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:58:16.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好因為多人爭就放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />份份筍工都一定多人爭<br />\n<br />\n不過覺得自己數理廢就算鳩數啦，唔好講M2個d層次啦，入得可能至少要有個物理 mphil <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccdb90df1d449e2d709c1cbfb7affa3ae7b40f4","tid":107861,"uid":14417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"而家讀緊咩？nursing?"},{"pid":"d28dfcfc062af572eb164dbf6d51170c127a42a6","tid":107861,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:02:12.000Z","msg":"in過幾次都唔得<br />\nphys真係好緊要 math反而唔係好重要<br />\n入面好似都係phys佬多"},{"pid":"be811f7ea48672c9274cda773a58f3e0a0def202","tid":107861,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"大學要修physics先入到<br />\n<br />\n最好仲要識電腦同image processing"},{"pid":"de0b9a113fd952125b4c86cbf79bd39df06b1092","tid":107861,"uid":76144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"我細個一直以為讀地理就可以喺天文台做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b97150c5979a53f28ced20381a3b1bc68b4d8a","tid":107861,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我細個一直以為讀地理就可以喺天文台做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：地理系畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9e9d961093d6ec41907e0900edf4e7b91bb59a","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你有冇諗過依份工適唔適合你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但計興趣黎講呢份工已經響我心目中排第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76c55a56bf626d80786ea3087a78b36e40eed2f","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁又唔好因為多人爭就放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />份份筍工都一定多人爭<br />\n<br />\n不過覺得自己數理廢就算鳩數啦，唔好講M2個d層次啦，入得可能至少要有個物理 mphil <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放心 我好有自知之明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71ddf47cf7cb88a355ece4429cd7be95a8818a4","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家讀緊咩？nursing?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5de271459d8f528d9bcb1e1a6c9b30f31df5953","tid":107861,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>in過幾次都唔得<br />\nphys真係好緊要 math反而唔係好重要<br />\n入面好似都係phys佬多</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打係math佬定phys佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873c331a682b03604420529fa0926e74dbdb19ec","tid":107861,"uid":78023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"有朋友做過 phy佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5972fa142227c9e0d0f80019f4c3b01496284b7","tid":107861,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:26:49.000Z","msg":"要十項全能數理化IT乜叉都識<br />\n仲要成績好學歷高<br />\n其實都幾癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c950ccacdf15b09e9846ca61c5e5c9ae54424c","tid":107861,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T13:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>in過幾次都唔得<br />\nphys真係好緊要 math反而唔係好重要<br />\n入面好似都係phys佬多</blockquote><br />\n咁巴打係math佬定phys佬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmath佬<br />\n啲phys一早掉鬼晒 次次都俾人問到口啞啞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}